OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClouding
OL,6,Fover through the evening. Mostly dry
OL,7,Fin the north and east with the odd
OL,8,Fspot of rain, occasionally heavy
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain in the west. Strong
OL,10,Fsoutheast coastal wind.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy at first as bands of
OL,13,Frain push northeast. Showers follow
OL,14,Ffrom the west, some heavy and
OL,15,Fthundery. Chance of a few brighter
OL,16,Fbreaks in shelter.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
