OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FShowers continue Thursday, heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. A further rain band pushes
OL,8,Fnortheast Friday with showers
OL,9,Ffollowing later. Showers or longer
OL,10,Fspells of rain on Saturday. Windy at
OL,11,Ftimes.
